{"tid":498781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[消委會] 3款口罩細菌過濾效率高於99.9% 邊2款口罩唔過關？","createTime":"2017-12-14T06:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T15:01:34.000Z","uid":72478,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9bedf6fca63261957019f31c6b7bba3942ab7f29","tid":498781,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171214/57579331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57579331&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b5334acf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171214%2F57579331&h=13b5af5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171214/57579331</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消委會測試發現，巿面口罩價格可相差逾百倍，但價格與產品質素未必有直接關聯，例如最貴樣本（36元）總評分只有3.5分，反而一個樣本僅售0.75元，卻獲最高的總評分5分。另外，有部分樣本的細菌過濾效率低於聲稱，甚至有2款樣本細菌過濾效率未達基本防護級別，當中有1款標明「高效細菌過濾」字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表現最佳的3款口罩為「Elleair超強阻隔PM2.5成人口罩（標準）」、「麥迪康SPSHMK2585彩色生活口罩耳掛式」以及「理的外科手術口罩」，其測試樣本的細菌過濾效率全部高於99.9%，當中麥迪康有4個樣本測試時更是完全檢測不到有細菌穿過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513227979_a396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513227979_a396.jpg&h=d34c0b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n表現最佳的3款口罩，左起為「Elleair超強阻隔PM2.5成人口罩（標準）」、「麥迪康SPSHMK2585彩色生活口罩耳掛式」以及「理的外科手術口罩」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171214/large/1513223027_ab04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171214%2Flarge%2F1513223027_ab04.jpg&h=b71a6e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總評分最低的2款口罩，圖左只有2分，但寫有「高效細菌過濾」字眼；圖右只有1分。"},{"pid":"5d0ffebb5a8514fb776fb3d2c64ea3405771d54e","tid":498781,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e44a0936e69816baeeb6fcc8c60f09e8cded4f","tid":498781,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76f9b498a74d71ea73d7a75d1f41a06c01b85c63","tid":498781,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:12:02.000Z","msg":"最右邊果隻用咁耐都覺得流流地<br />\n<br />\n原來都咁堅"},{"pid":"8b57d7bc8f54950be594058768dbfcf589c923f8","tid":498781,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8ba8d465e86b9c72a47c57a28c982e272881ee","tid":498781,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"右一個隻原來咁堅，真係又平又好用"},{"pid":"cbf0431f526e6ab5a37a4da1c29ac8e1e8071e9b","tid":498781,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最右邊果隻用咁耐都<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得</span>流流地<br />\n<br />\n原來都咁堅</blockquote><br />\n覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇讀科學嘅人講句野都真係廢d"},{"pid":"c458d0cc3683a67c4545d8ed1d46290c268b1c7a","tid":498781,"uid":79627,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最右邊果隻用咁耐都<span style=\"color: red;\">覺得</span>流流地<br />\n<br />\n原來都咁堅</blockquote><br />\n覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇讀科學嘅人講句野都真係廢d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先  邊個話你聽我冇讀科學<br />\n第二  覺得，係我觀察佢個膠袋包裝，紙盒，綜合嘅感覺上認爲流流哋<br />\n<br />\n唔通吓吓都要做實驗？<br />\n<br />\n有個人感覺有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45740b3e8037e