>\n醫護用, 一定係用3層無紡布口罩"},{"pid":"15672964303072e23583180ad0192bbc449cf339","tid":498781,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最右邊果隻用咁耐都覺得流流地<br />\n<br />\n原來都咁堅</blockquote><br />\n最右邊個隻, 根本就唔係用嚟防菌.<br />\n呢隻只會係美容院用, 純綷用黎防噴口水, 同埋防口氣.<br />\n醫護用, 一定係用3層無紡布口罩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.scenery.com.hk/media/catalog/product/cache/2/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/r/product-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scenery.com.hk%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F2%2Fimage%2F9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95%2Fp%2Fr%2Fproduct-2.jpg&h=4fa993f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家用呢隻，唔知掂唔掂呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b3e1faebb681def2d48130b34bf5b8d4c77cb2","tid":498781,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"以前係最右邊個間做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a8d55a07536cb672a2a3faaa4fd6d7c74a872b","tid":498781,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最右邊果隻用咁耐都覺得流流地<br />\n<br />\n原來都咁堅</blockquote><br />\n最右邊個隻, 根本就唔係用嚟防菌.<br />\n呢隻只會係美容院用, 純綷用黎防噴口水, 同埋防口氣.<br />\n醫護用, 一定係用3層無紡布口罩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.scenery.com.hk/media/catalog/product/cache/2/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/p/r/product-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scenery.com.hk%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F2%2Fimage%2F9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95%2Fp%2Fr%2Fproduct-2.jpg&h=4fa993f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家用呢隻，唔知掂唔掂呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港大部分政府老人院同公立醫院都用佢<br />\nsource:老母係其中一間老人院做"},{"pid":"353eb5de9bcdfb46be7e4c7a68b5f101c52a960b","tid":498781,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor